## Description
When presenting the result of an image in portrait format, the images overflow the screen.

### Steps to reproduce (on 1600x900 screen)
- Upload image in portrait format (https://mymodernmet.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/gabrielius-khiterer-stray-cats-4.jpg)
- Click the 'colorize button'

### Observed behavior
images overflow screen, scrollbar is displayed

### Expected behavior
images fit on screen, no scrollbar is displayed, complete background is gray

### Screenshot
![Screenshot](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/)


## Acceptance criteria
* The service works as described in 'Expected behavior'

## Definition of done
* All acceptance criteria met
* Documentation completed
* Peer code review passed
